content:
Share Catalog Item Links to Customers with Einstein Copilot (Beta)

Use Einstein Copilot in Service Catalog to build custom actions that resolve customer contact reasons by sharing URL links to the items in your catalog. Through a generative AI-powered conversational experience, Copilot determines which of your catalog items resolve the contact reason and then provides the customer a URL link to the item in you catalog.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with Service Cloud, the Customer Service Catalog add-on, and the Einstein for Service add-on. Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience.

To use this feature, you must have the Service Catalog Builder perm set and Use Einstein Copilot for Salesforce User perm set. 

How: Build a custom Copilot action using the Service Catalog Item action type for any catalog item that contains orchestration or screen flows in their fulfillment. First, enable Einstein generative AI and turn on Einstein Copilot for Salesforce from Setup. Then, from the Catalog Settings page in Setup, turn on Catalog Item Sharing.
